    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>无数子弹对抗无尽混乱的外星人</i></h2>《Survivors of the Dawn》是一款类Rogue的生存弹幕游戏。在混乱中用<strong>无数子弹轰击无数敌人</strong>！死亡、进化、探索终端、在混乱中解锁武器道具的强化，找到从黎明中崛起的协同力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >稀有度、升级与武器库系统</h2>购买物品并修改你的武器，消灭<strong>无数敌人</strong>！在<strong>武器库</strong>中，缩短冷却时间加快重装，提升射击速度，用<strong>穿透力</strong>削弱敌群，或者提升<strong>子弹数量</strong>以造成更大的爆炸。同时，<strong>稀有度</strong>越高，<strong>升级</strong>越强大——但代价也更大。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/d19f7f6e0a5b6eaae4b901de5da5e49a.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/d19f7f6e0a5b6eaae4b901de5da5e49a.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/d19f7f6e0a5b6eaae4b901de5da5e49a.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器与物品组合搭配</h2>升级武器，堆叠物品，混合搭配，消灭敌群。额外的盟友或闪亮的强化道具？只需最大化一些武器类别即可。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/9b2434436c5f2509823e60e0e21cdc17.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/9b2434436c5f2509823e60e0e21cdc17.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/9b2434436c5f2509823e60e0e21cdc17.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽情挑战终端</h2>清理终端：用<strong>蜘蛛机器人</strong>治疗，或在混乱中找到<strong>S.O.S</strong>。想挑战自己？召唤更多敌群。难度领先？前往<strong>黄色未知信号</strong>，如果足够幸运，你可能会找到<strong><i>重掷或跳过</i></strong>的机会！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/52d98c8f2f39f1adec4f617fd658e6eb.poster.avif?t=1765396692\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/52d98c8f2f39f1adec4f617fd658e6eb.webm?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285630/extras/52d98c8f2f39f1adec4f617fd658e6eb.mp4?t=1765396692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>哦，天哪……如果不在下一次挑战前花费你的<i><strong>赏金币</strong></i>，元进度就难以保证！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队</h2>indieGiant Games是一家有着<strong>宏大</strong>创意的<i>微型</i>工作室，专注于制作趣味性十足、核心玩法为导向、拥有高制作价值的独立游戏。《SotD》是该工作室的首款PC游戏，由独立开发者独立完成。",
